Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:01.70,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Are you happy at your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.40,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yes, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What makes you so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:10.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,You know, playing and talking with my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.57,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,That’s good! It is a good thing to like school, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.26,0:00:17.28,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Were you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:24.53,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Not really, because I didn’t have many friends there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.70,0:00:29.21,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You feel sad without friends at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:33.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Yeah... I’m sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:35.36,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,That story reminds you of a bad memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:44.66,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly wasn’t good memory, but that’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:52.92,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I actually feel sorry for my past, but my current job makes me think that was a good experience for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:54.68,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Good experience?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:57.37,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:05.86,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,For example, such an experience is sometimes so useful to analyze the psychology of those who doesn’t want to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.82,0:01:07.62,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It sounds difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:16.14,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I’m talking about myself now! Whenever I talk about my job, I tend to get lost in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:20.24,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I guess I would make a better patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:26.37,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Ok, let’s change the subject. Well, what is your best friend like?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.70,0:01:30.37,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,She is really cheerful and nice to me. I’m really happy around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.37,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:34.72,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:40.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay... Misato. What do you usually do together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:46.14,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,We read books together at her place and I listen to her playing violin sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Wow, she can play the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.14,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:51.74,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,She must be a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:55.60,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Why don’t you come over with her next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:00.02,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,But she is so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:02.80,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,So shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:08.81,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Maybe... I’ll ask her anyway. I’m guessing she wouldn’t want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.98,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, I wish she could.
